{{#*inline "content"}}
<h1 style="color: #2E7D32; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
    ✓ Extension Request Approved!
</h1>

<p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>

<p>We're pleased to inform you that your course access extension request has been approved! You now have <strong>{{extensionDays}} additional days</strong> to complete your course.</p>

<div style="background: #F8FAFC; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Extension Details:</h3>
    <ul class="features">
        <li>📅 <strong>{{extensionDays}} days</strong> added to your access period</li>
        <li>📚 Course: {{courseName}}</li>
        <li>⏳ New expiration date: {{expirationDate}}</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="button-container">
    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" style="
        background: #FF502A;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    ">Continue Learning Now →</a>
</div>

<p style="margin: 25px 0;">Need more time or having trouble accessing the course?<br>
Our support team is ready to help at <a href="{{mailto:supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>

<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666;">
    *Your extended access period starts from your original expiration date
</p>
{{/inline}}